1.1
log
@Initial revision
@
text
@/*      $OpenBSD: wdcreg.h,v 1.7 2002/06/15 10:59:06 gluk Exp $     */
/*	$NetBSD: wdcreg.h,v 1.22 1999/03/07 14:02:54 bouyer Exp $	*/

/*-
